{"content":"<li class=\"n-box-item date-title\" data-end=\"1441684799\" data-start=\"1441598400\" data-txt=\"Sunday, December 22, 2019\">Monday, September  7, 2015</li><li class=\"n-box-item sa-box-item\" data-id=\"2764666\" data-ts=\"1441626108\"><div class=\"media media-overflow-fix\"><div class=\"media-left\"><a class=\"box-ticker\" href=\"/symbol/\" target=\"_blank\"></a></div><div class=\"media-body\"><h4 class=\"media-heading\"><a href=\"/news/2764666-shanghai-down-sharply-pboc-sees-end-to-correction\" sasource=\"on_the_move_news_fidelity\" target=\"_blank\">Shanghai down sharply; PBOC sees end to &quot;correction&quot;</a></h4><ul>\n<li>Closed for holiday last Thursday and Friday, Shanghai<font color=\"red\"> fell 2.5%</font> after reopening on Monday. The Hang Seng <font color=\"red\">fell 1.2%</font>.</li>\n<li>Beijing on Monday <a href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/china-cuts-2014-economic-growth-to-73-from-74-2015-09-07\" target=\"_blank\">shaved 2014</a> (not a typo) GDP growth to 7.3% from 7.4%. The government's target for 2015 is 7%, a target the <a href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/china-on-track-to-hit-economic-growth-target-ndrc-2015-09-07\" target=\"_blank\">NRDC today said</a> the country is on track to match.</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/chinas-central-bank-chief-predicts-end-nigh-for-market-rout-1441543186\" target=\"_blank\">Speaking at the G-20 meeting</a> of finance ministers and central bankers, PBOC boss Zhou Xiaochuan acknowledged a (now burst) bubble in Chinese equities, but said the \"correction in the stock market is almost done.\"</li>\n<li>The country's forex reserves <a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-09-07/china-s-foreign-exchange-reserves-fall-in-august-on-yuan-support\" target=\"_blank\">dropped by a record $93.9B</a> in August to $3.56T as Beijing countered capital outflows and the weakening yuan. Forex reserves have been steadily declining since about the middle of 2014.</li>\n<li>ETFs: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/fxi\" title=\"iShares China Large-Cap ETF\">FXI</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ashr\" title=\"Deutsche X-trackers Harvest CSI 300 China A-Shares ETF\">ASHR</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ewh\" title=\"iShares MSCI Hong Kong ETF\">EWH</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/caf\" title=\"Morgan Stanley China A Share Fund\">CAF</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/yinn\" title=\"Direxion Daily FTSE China Bull 3X Shares ETF\">YINN</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/pgj\" title=\"PowerShares Golden Dragon China Portfolio ETF\">PGJ</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/gxc\" title=\"SPDR S&amp;P China ETF\">GXC</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/fxp\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort FTSE China 25 ETF\">FXP</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/yang\" title=\"Direxion Daily FTSE China Bear 3x Shares ETF\">YANG</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/chn\" title=\"China Fund\">CHN</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/pek\" title=\"Market Vectors ChinaAMC A-Share ETF\">PEK</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/mchi\" title=\"iShares MSCI China ETF\">MCHI</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/tdf\" title=\"Templeton Dragon Fund\">TDF</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/xpp\" title=\"ProShares Ultra FTSE China 25 ETF\">XPP</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/yao\" title=\"Guggenheim China All-Cap ETF\">YAO</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/gch\" title=\"Greater China Fund\">GCH</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ashs\" title=\"Deutsche X-trackers Harvest CSI 500 China-A Shares Small Cap ETF\">ASHS</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/yxi\" title=\"ProShares Short FTSE China 50 ETF\">YXI</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/cn\" title=\"Deutsche X-trackers Harvest MSCI All China Equity ETF\">CN</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/chxf\" title=\"WisdomTree China Dividend ex-Financials ETF\">CHXF</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/fca\" title=\"First Trust China AlphaDEX ETF\">FCA</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/cnxt\" title=\"Market Vectors ChinaAMC SME-ChiNext ETF\">CNXT</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/chna\" title=\"PowerShares China A - Share Portfolio ETF\">CHNA</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ewhs\" title=\"iShares MSCI Hong Kong Small-Cap ETF\">EWHS</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/kba\" title=\"KraneShares Bosera MSCI China A ETF\">KBA</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/fchi\" title=\"iShares FTSE China (HK-Listed) Index ETF\">FCHI</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/jfc\" title=\"JPMorgan China Region Fund, Inc.\">JFC</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/fhk\" title=\"First Trust Hong Kong AlphaDex ETF\">FHK</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/afty\" title=\"CSOP FTSE China A50 ETF\">AFTY</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/chau\" title=\"Direxion Daily CSI 300 China A Share Bull 2X ETF\">CHAU</a>\n</li>\n</ul><div class=\"tiny-share-widget\" data-id=\"2764666\" data-linked=\"Shanghai down sharply; PBOC sees end to &quot;correction&quot;\" data-tweet=\"$FXI $ASHR $EWH - Shanghai down sharply; PBOC sees end to &quot;correction&quot; https://seekingalpha.com/news/2764666-shanghai-down-sharply-pboc-sees-end-to-correction?source=tweet\" data-url=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/2764666-shanghai-down-sharply-pboc-sees-end-to-correction\"><div class=\"icon share-btn c-email\" title=\"Email a friend\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-twitter\" title=\"Share on Twitter\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-facebook\" title=\"Share on Facebook\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-linkedin\" title=\"Share on Linkedin\">&nbsp;</div></div><span class=\"mc_gray_separator\">|</span>  7:41 AM <span class='mc_gray_separator'>|</span> <span class='comments